Winterfell Castle. 

The home of the Stark family stood for millenia in the North. It was then destroyed shortly after Theon Greyjoy forced Bran Stark to yield the castle to him. 

Winterfell can be explored at Castle Ward : 

https://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/visit/northern-ireland/castle-ward
